		    CRO - Closure Reopening
	(for improving performance of Java or Scala closures)
		       © 2010 Erik Søe Sørensen

Directory structure:

+-+ doc/	Look in here for more information.
  |
  + ext/	External dependencies (third-party .jar files we use)
  |
  + src/	The source code.
    |
    +- main/
    |  |
    |  +- scala/
    |     |
    |     +- cro/	Where the source code lives.
    |
    +- test/
       |
       +- scala/
          |
          +- cro/	Where the test code lives.
